{"type": "article", "id": 2205, "title": "Victoria’s Secret 2014 秋冬运动系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:27:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222253T0qI6tjxbVBNrgMH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">内衣品牌 Victoria’s Secret 发布 2014 秋冬女性运动内衣系列，请来了 Candice Swanepoel 和Lily Aldrige 两位超模，穿上运动型内衣及相关运动配件，体现女性运动的健康美。比起专业运动品牌的内衣，Victoria’s Secret 在兼具功能性的同时，也相当重视外观上的设计，提供多种印花图案及配色，胸前的双层拉链设计既能塑身，又能保证运动中的贴合性，同时方便穿脱。售价 54.5 美元起，</span><a href=\"https://www.victoriassecret.com/victorias-secret-sport/sports-bras\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134910vXfbwSRmGrhIaTJg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134911B4vNbKXyT9oqQOne.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.121875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134911gAneXLqDGw9VosfB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134912Q6h2lgU1HO9BeMXD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}